Title: Too Tough to Die
Plot: A woman is abducted from a mall parking garage, then raped, beaten, shot and left for dead. Catherine and Warrick are given boxes of evidence from a shooting that goes to trial in four days, and they must re-prove the case.
GuestStars: Netfa Perry, Timothy Carhart, Katy Boyer, Ntare Mwine, Aldis Hodge, Andy Taylor, Micelle Anne Johnson, Gary Bristow, Geoff Meed, Mark Collver, Larry Bagby III, Ed Patterson
